INSERT INTO `challengers2026` VALUES (1,'Matt Maasdam','MAASDAM, MATT','D','MI',7,'https://mattmaasdam.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/matt-maasdam-maasdam-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-08 14:43:51','2025-09-08 17:00:51','maasdam.png','I’m a Navy SEAL who served Presidents of both parties in Iraq, Afghanistan, and at the White House. I’ve dedicated my life to service, and now I’m continuing my service by stepping up to represent our families here in Michigan.\n\nI’m running for Congress to bring a different kind of leadership– one rooted in hard work, courage, and integrity. I believe in the Michigan Dream– where if you work hard, you can build a good life and get ahead.'),(2,'BRIDGET BRINK','BRINK, BRIDGET','D','MI',7,'https://bridgetbrink.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/bridget-brink-1','2025-09-08 16:54:45','2025-09-10 12:40:19','brink.png','Democratic challenger for MI-7. Cash on hand: $484,664'),(3,'Pete Barlow','BARLOW, PETE','D','VA',6,'https://www.pete-barlow.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/pete-barlow-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-08 17:05:23','2025-09-08 17:07:09','barlow.png','Ben Cline is nothing but a cheerleader. He says yes to every policy Trump wants. Never questioning. Never fighting for his constituents. Never defending the Constitution. Cline has become a lapdog of the White House. He doesn’t even try to represent the Valley. And he’s a coward. He refuses to face the voters in public meetings and town halls.\n<p>\nPete is the opposite. Pete is a leader. While co-founding a tech startup and working on his farm, Pete will be doing what a member of Congress should do. He will be jumping in his 13-year-old truck to host #peopletalk2pete gatherings and listening to his neighbors. He is eager to hear their ideas about what they need from their government and what changes they would like to see.\n\n'),(4,'KEN MITCHELL','MITCHELL, KEN','D','VA',6,'https://www.kenmitchellforvirginia.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/ken-mitchell-for-va-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-08 17:12:09','2025-09-10 12:40:19','mitchell.jpg','Democratic challenger for VA-6. Cash on hand: $53,935'),(5,'Shannon Taylor','TAYLOR, SHANNON','D','VA',1,'https://shannontaylorva.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/shannon-taylor-1','2025-09-08 17:18:54','2025-09-08 17:18:54','taylor.jpg','Shannon Taylor has spent the past 13 years as Henrico County’s top prosecutor protecting families and keeping our streets safe. She’s taken on violent criminals, fraudsters and drug dealers—never backing down from the toughest fights.\n\nNow Shannon is running for Congress in Virginia’s 1st District to take on career politician Rob Wittman, who has sold out working families to special interests and the ultra-wealthy. Shannon will fight to lower costs, enforce our laws and protect our healthcare.'),(6,'BLAKE GENDEBIEN','GENDEBIEN, BLAKE','D','NY',21,'https://blakegendebienforcongress.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/blake-gendebien-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-09 12:21:51','2025-09-10 12:40:19','gendebien.jpg','Democratic challenger for NY-21. Cash on hand: $1,961,650'),(7,'PETER CHATZKY','CHATZKY, PETER','D','NY',17,'https://chatzkyforcongress.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/peter-chatzky-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-09 12:41:36','2025-09-10 12:40:19','chatzky.jpg','Democratic challenger for NY-17. Cash on hand: $674,353'),(8,'CAIT CONLEY','CONLEY, CAIT','D','NY',17,'https://caitconley.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/cait-conley-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-09 12:45:30','2025-09-10 12:40:19','conley.jpg','Democratic challenger for NY-17. Cash on hand: $613,787'),(9,'TROY MCGHIE','MCGHIE, TROY','D','NY',11,'https://troymcghie.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/troy-mcghie-1','2025-09-09 12:51:25','2025-09-10 12:40:19','mcghie.jpg','Democratic challenger for NY-11. Cash on hand: $22,939'),(10,'Gian Jones','JONES, GIAN','D','NY',4,'','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/gian-a--jones-for-congress-1','2025-09-09 12:56:47','2025-09-09 12:57:45','gianjones.jpg','Gian is a father, community leader, and business owner for over 25 years. He has the background and experience to connect with and win over the moderate and independent voters who will decide this election.\n\n\n\nNY-04 is considered one of the most flippable districts in the nation. Chip in now to help us launch our campaign to flip NY-04 blue!'),(11,'Lukas Ventouras','VENTOURAS, LUKAS','D','NY',1,'https://amh1234.wixsite.com/ventouras4congress','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lukas-ventouras-1','2025-09-09 13:12:14','2025-09-09 13:44:02','ventouras.jpg','My name is Lukas Ventouras, and I am a first time candidate running for Congress in NY-01. Sprawling almost all of Suffolk County, New York, from Huntington to The Hamptons, including the Shinnecock Nation and Shelter Island, it is expansive, and diverse, both culturally and socioeconomically, making it a microcosm of the US.\n\nIn recent years, many Democrats have tried, and failed, to win this district, ever since Democrat Tim Bishop lost his bid for a 7th term to Lee Zeldin in 2014.\n\nNobody has approached this race like I have, with humility, grit, and meticulous hard work, starting as early as I have, visiting places which are neglected and taken for granted. They tell me I cant win, but they’re wrong. They just haven’t seen someone as passionate, who is willing to work as hard as I am. They tell me I can’t win but they’re wrong. We are going to win, and we’re going to do it together. '),(12,'Josh Taveras','TAVERAS, JOSH','D','NY',2,'https://www.joshtaverasforcongress.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/joshua-taveras-1','2025-09-09 13:20:00','2025-09-09 13:20:00','taveras.jpg','Welcome to the campaign for Josh Taveras, a first-generation Dominican-American, proud son of Long Island, and Democratic candidate for New York’s 2nd Congressional District.\n\nJosh isn’t a politician. He’s a neighbor, a fighter, and a survivor of a system that was never built for people like us. Raised in Copiague by an immigrant family, Josh has lived the struggles too many in NY-2 face, poverty, loss, food insecurity, and being the voice for his parents in a country that often treated them like outsiders.\n\nNow, he’s stepping up to give our communities the voice they deserve in Washington.\n\n'),(1421,'ESTHER KIM VARET','VARET, ESTHER KIM','D','CA',40,'https://www.estherkimvaret.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/esther-kim-varet-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19','varet.jpg','Democratic challenger for CA-40. Cash on hand: $1,309,000'),(1422,'REBECCA COOKE','COOKE, REBECCA','D','WI',3,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19',NULL,'Democratic challenger for WI-3. Cash on hand: $1,267,170'),(1423,'EILEEN LAUBACHER','LAUBACHER, EILEEN','D','CO',4,'https://www.eileenforcolorado.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/eileen-laubacher-1','2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19','laubacher.jpg','Democratic challenger for CO-4. Cash on hand: $1,092,170'),(1424,'SHAUN FINNIE','FINNIE, SHAUN','D','TX',2,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19',NULL,'Democratic challenger for TX-2. Cash on hand: $1,018,460'),(1425,'JONATHAN TREBLE','TREBLE, JONATHAN','D','AZ',1,'http://trebleforaz.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/jonathan-treble-1?refcode=directory','2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19','treble.jpg','Democratic challenger for AZ-1. Cash on hand: $871,511'),(1426,'CHRISTINA BOHANNAN','BOHANNAN, CHRISTINA','D','IA',1,'https://www.bohannanforcongress.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/christina-bohannan-for-congress-2?refcode=directory','2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19','bohannan.jpg','Democratic challenger for IA-1. Cash on hand: $819,588'),(1427,'MANNY RUTINEL','RUTINEL, MANNY','D','CO',8,'https://www.mannyforcolorado.com/','https://secure.actblue.com/donate/manny-rutinel-1','2025-09-09 14:16:15','2025-09-10 12:40:19','rutinel.jpg','Democr